title: Index of the Wholesale Prices of Finished Goods, Consumer, Other Nondurables for United States
notes:
For A Description Of Wholesale Price Indexes By Stage Of Processing And The Weights Allocated To Finished Consumer Other Nondurable Goods, See Bls, "Wholesale Prices And Price Indexes," January 1967 Final, And February, 1967 Final, Pp. 116-117 And Pp. 125-127." As Of June 1966, Bls Bulletin No. 1513 Shows Monthly Data For 1963. Consumer Nondurables Excludes Foods.
